From Michael Sells Subject Re PLEASE SHOW UP IN WASHINGTON DC FOR BOSNIA MAY Subject Re PLEASE SHOW UP IN WASHINGTON DC FOR BOSNIA MAY From Nick Jovanovic Date May In article Nick Jovanovic writes In article Michael Sells writes I find it interesting that Major finds the genocide of two million Muslims in Bosnia acceptable Now you are actually claiming that Muslims have been killed in B H Please substantiate this utterly ridiculous No I'm not claiming have been We are in the middle of the genocide process that Major has given yet another green light Mladic seems to have most of what he wants but Boban is just getting his appetite Because Mladic refuses to allow international observers to inspect mass grave sites and killing centers in places like Foca Brcko and Visegrad it will be years before we have an accurate account of the number In practical terms it would be impossible to kill all There just isn't the kind of machinery of crematoria and gas chambers and transportation lines that the Nazis took YEARS to And remember the Nazis killed minorities in the countries they To actually kill of the population requires extreme genocidal But I do claim that the goal of the genocide is the systematic annihilation of Bosnian Muslim culture by killing as many as is feasible by rape by torture by the demolition of mosques libraries and culture artificts the burning and renaming of villages the shelling of So that there won't be any of the or so Muslims whose lives have not been shattered by the genocide though they still may be And Major not only finds this acceptable he helps it along by making sure that the victims don't have arms to defend Nick Michael Sells Department of Religion Haverford College Haverford Pa